      "created_at": "2018-12-28T13:03:18.202Z",
      "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Neuer\" data-post=\"17\" data-topic=\"4516\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/neuer/48/109_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Neuer:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Jane gati te heqin dhe palloshin nqs jua ve ti si kusht.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>palloshin jane gati ta heqin, por nuk jane dakord te heqin marlonin. As vete Pjeri nuk eshte dakord te heqe marlonin, se do ngelet pa bo qef. Nuk ka lezet jeta pa i çik marlon ngambrapa!</p>",
